  "keyFeatures": [
    "WebGL2-based instanced sprite rendering for minimal draw calls",
    "Stateless, data-driven rendering API with no scene graph",
    "Hierarchical transform matrix stack with save/restore",
    "Flexible texture system: images, render textures, and text textures",
    "Custom GLSL shader support via CustomGlShader with padding/filter chains",
    "Particle emitter with animated attributes (color, speed, scale, velocity)",
    "Built-in primitives: sprites, rects, circles, lines, and polygons",
    "Stencil-buffer masking (EQUAL / NOT_EQUAL)",
    "Offscreen render textures with pixel read-back",
    "Multiple blend modes: NORMAL, ADD, MULTIPLY, SCREEN, ERASE",
    "Scissor clipping for rectangular clip regions",
    "Texture atlas / sprite sheet splitting utilities",
    "Device-pixel-ratio-aware rendering with CanvasItem and Viewport scale modes"
  ],
